t;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&gt; 20.000.000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;15%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; &lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LƯU Ý: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Thời gian bắt đầu hiển thị quảng cáo sau 3 ngày kể từ ngày ký hợp đồng. ( Thời gian 3 ngày để lên chi tiết nội dung quảng cáo và tối ưu website ).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Thời gian báo cáo kết quả chạy quảng cáo vào 10h sáng t